BELIEVE I DO.

375
00:26:50,328 --> 00:26:52,430
OUT OF MY WAY.

376
00:26:59,137 --> 00:27:00,405
MS. GENEREAU,
MS. GENEREAU.

377
00:27:00,438 --> 00:27:02,373
OVER HERE.

378
00:27:02,407 --> 00:27:04,442
