HE'S GOT ONE SEAT OPEN.

384
00:27:14,953 --> 00:27:16,988
COME ON.

385
00:27:27,032 --> 00:27:29,868
HEY, CAN YOU HEAR ME?

386
00:27:29,901 --> 00:27:34,272
- SIR, DO YOU HEAR ME?
- YEAH, I FUCKING HEAR YOU.

387
00:27:34,305 --> 00:27:36,307
